<section class="headersection">
  <h1>Hvorfor er genbrug<br /><span> løsningen?</span></h1>
  <p>
    Fremtiden kalder på mere genbrug, hvis vi skal løse plastikkrisen. Forstå
    hvorfor, at omfattende genbrugssystemer er en af de mest effektive løsninger
    til at løse plastikkrisen.
  </p>
</section>
<article>
  <div class="video-container">
    <iframe
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7eivTQkBYvo?si=4X2BvPIswXobDr97"
      title="YouTube video player"
      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
      allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </div>
</article>

<style>
  .maxwidth {
    max-width: 1650px;
    margin-left: 0;
    padding: var(--spacing-text-padding-vertical, 2rem);
  }

  .headersection {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    max-width: 100%;
    padding-left: var(--article-padding-horizontal);
    padding-right: var(--article-padding-horizontal);
    padding-top: 10rem;
    gap: var(--article-gap);
  }
  h1 {
    color: var(--header-color);
    font-size: clamp(
      var(--font-size-header-small),
      5vw,
      var(--font-size-header-large)
    );
    line-height: var(--line-height-header);
  }
  span {
    color: var(--highlight-color);
  }

  p {
    color: var(--paragraph-color);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  article {
    max-width: 1650px;
    margin: auto; /* Centers the content */
    padding: var(--spacing-section-padding-horzontal, 8rem);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; /* Aligns children elements to the center */
  }

  .video-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    padding-top: 50%; /* Maintain aspect ratio for larger screens */
  }

  .video-container iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  /* Media query for mobile screens */
  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    article {
      max-width: 100%; /* Adjust max-width for smaller screens */
      padding: var(--container-padding-top-bottom, 32px)
        var(--container-padding-left-right, 64px);
    }

    .video-container {
      height: 250px;
      padding-top: 0;
    }
    .headersection {
      max-width: 120%;
      padding: 2rem;
      padding-top: 7rem;
    }
    h1 {
      line-height: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
